data.description: Welcome to 1102 Albemarle Way, a magnificent family home that offers an exceptional blend of elegance, comfort, and modern convenience. Situated in the heart of the sought after Brookwood school district. This 5-bedroom, 4-bathroom home boasts a generous square feet of living space, providing room for the whole family. Step inside to be greeted by a 2 story foyer and discover an open and bright floor plan featuring high ceilings, large windows, and beautiful finishes throughout. The main floor boasts spacious living areas that flow seamlessly from room to room, creating an inviting and open atmosphere. Whether you're hosting a family gathering or a quiet night in, this layout accommodates your lifestyle effortlessly. The kitchen seamlessly flows into the dining and living areas, allowing you to engage with family and guests while preparing meals. It's perfect for entertaining and creating lasting memories complete with double oven, ample counter space and a breakfast bar. The upstairs hosts 3 secondary bedrooms, a full bath, laundry room and The owners suite is a sanctuary of relaxation, featuring a spacious walk-in closet and a spa-like en-suite bathroom with a soaking tub, separate shower, and double vanity. Enjoy the finished basement that offers a full finish bath, flex spaces, and room for storage. Located in a quiet and friendly neighborhood that offers 2 pools, a kiddie wet area, sidewalks, 10 tennis courts, a lake, clubhouse and two playgrounds. This home is just minutes away from schools, parks, shopping, dining and major commuting routes, providing an unparalleled sense of convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your family's new home. Schedule a showing today.
